Počkajte chvíľu.

674
00:50:31,910 --> 00:50:33,120
Yi Ryung.

675
00:50:34,600 --> 00:50:35,930
Tae Gong Sil?

676
00:50:35,930 --> 00:50:37,430
Počúvaj, Yi Ryung.

677
00:50:37,440 --> 00:50:41,030
